content:
GTA+ Members can claim the Ride or Die Gaiter and SA Denim Biker Jacket for free through December 9.

Show normies your anarchist edge by rocking the Ride or Die Gaiter and SA Denim Biker Jacket. This killer combo not only keeps the wind at bay while tearing up the streets in your new Nagasaki Shinobi, but also helps you blend in with your fellow rebels.

GTA+ Membership automatically renews monthly, cancel anytime. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
